item.title: MegerConflict
item.description: Chapter X MegerConflict hint: Updates were rejected because the tip of your current branch is behind hint: its remote counterpart. Integrate the remote changes (e.g. hint: ‘git pull …’) before pushing again. hint: See the ‘Note about fast-forwards’ in ‘git push –help’ for details. 解决 勾选强制覆盖已有的分支（可能会丢失改动），再点击上传，上传成功。 git push -u origin master -f Lorem Ipsum.
